# What is Web-hook
Web-hook is created in github or bitbucket to notify CI/CD tools when changes occur in repository to automatically build the updated code

# How a Web-hook work
Web-hook can be trigger whenever specific event occur on github.

# What is the benefit of webhook
With the help of webhook we can automate workflows using trigger that we can setup in webhook configuration, whenever particular event will happen automatically trigger will start its functionality.

